The testimony by Paups in Testimony 3 states, "That's why I... I used the gun I got from Lance...!" This implies Paups used a gun that was given by Lance. However, Evidence 13 is the Missing Model Gun. If this missing model gun is supposed to be the gun in question or if the missing model gun was linked to Lance, Paups claiming to have used a gun from Lance would contradict the fact that the gun is missing.

Hence, there is a contradiction between Evidence 13 (Missing Model Gun) and Testimony 3 (Paups stating that she used the gun she got from Lance).

